question: Where can I find fast food restaurant heading towards Polish Museum of America, Chicago, IL from King's Grove, IL, within a radius of 60 kilometers?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-87.656017 41.47522)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-87.66105 41.899674)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-87.656017 41.47522)',4326)::geography, 60000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-87.656017 41.47522)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
